text.ko_KR: 누군가나 뭔가를 찾는 거 아닐까?\.\. 흥분하지 마, 얘들아.<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]
text.ja_JP:
何か、人か物を探してるのかも？
\.\.\.みんな、落ち着いて。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]

message.en_US: Yummy...\. almost like the real thing!
message.pt_BR: Que delicia...\. quase como comida real!
message.de_DE: Hmmm... lecker...\. Fast wie das Echte!
message.ja_JP: おいしいです...\.本物みたいだ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]

message.en_US: \c[2][Delicious]\c[0]
message.pt_BR: \c[2][Delicioso]\c[0]
message.de_DE: \c[2][Lecker]\c[0]

message.en_US: So they finally support proper taste senses.\. That's great!
message.pt_BR: Ento eles finalmente suportam os sentidos gustativos adequados.\. Isso  timo!
message.de_DE: Also werden endlich richtige Geschmackssinne unterstützt.\. Find' ich toll!
message.zh_TW: 哦，他們終於實裝味覺系統了啊。\.真好！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]
message.zh_CN: 哦，他们终于实装味觉系统了啊。\.真好！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]
message.ko_KR: 드디어 맛이 느껴지는 기능도 넣었구나.\. 대단한걸!<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]
message.ja_JP:
てことは、やっと運営はまともな味覚を
組み込んだんだね。\.やったね！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]

message.en_US: I hope they'll add \c[3]Roquefort Cheese\c[0] as well.\. You have to try it!
message.pt_BR: Espero que eles adicionem tambm o \c[3]Queijo Roquefort\c[0].\. Vocs tem que experimentar!
message.de_DE: Hoffentlich fügen sie auch \c[3]Roquefort-Käse\c[0] hinzu.\. Den müsst ihr unbedingt probieren!
message.zh_TW: 希望他們哪天能加入\c[3]洛克福羊乳乾酪\c[0]。\.你一定得試試！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]
message.zh_CN:
希望他们哪天能加入\c[3]洛克福羊乳干酪\c[0]。\.你一定得试试！
<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]
message.ko_KR:
\c[3]로크포르 치즈\c[0]도 추가해 줬으면 좋겠네.\. 네가 먹어봤으면 좋겠어!
<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]
message.ja_JP:
\c[3]ロックフォールチーズ\c[0]も追加して
くれたらいいのに。\.食べてみてほしいな。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]

message.en_US: Oh no...
message.pt_BR: Ah no...
message.de_DE: Oh nein...

message.en_US: \c[2][I want to eat]\c[0]
message.pt_BR: \c[2][Eu quero comer]\c[0]
message.de_DE: \c[2][Möchte ich essen]\c[0]

message.en_US: No...\. you don't.
message.pt_BR: No...\. voc no quer.
message.de_DE: Nein...\. Das möchtest du nicht.
message.ja_JP: いや...\.やめた方が。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]

message.en_US: I'm sure that taste is impossible to simulate without breaking pain constraints.
message.pt_BR: Tenho certeza de que  impossvel simular o sabor sem quebrar as restries da dor.
message.de_DE: Ich bin davon überzeugt, dass es unmöglich ist, diesen Geschmack zu simulieren, ohne die Schmerzgrenze zu überschreiten.
message.zh_TW: 那玩意吃下去只會造成痛苦。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]
message.zh_CN: 那玩意吃下去只会造成痛苦。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]
message.ko_KR: 통증 제약을 풀지 않고서는 그 맛을 구현할 수 없을 거야.<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]
message.ja_JP:
あの味の模倣は、痛みの制限を
越えない限りは不可能でしょうね。<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]

message.en_US: Don't listen to him, Lea!
message.pt_BR: No ligue pra ele, Lea!
message.de_DE: Hör nicht auf ihn, Lea!
message.ja_JP: レア、トロニーの話は聞かなくていいよ！<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/01/12]

message.en_US: It may look horrible...\. it might also taste a bit horrible...
message.pt_BR: Pode parecer horrvel...\. e pode tambm ter um sabor um pouco horrvel...
message.de_DE: Er mag vielleicht scheußlich aussehen...\. er kann sogar etwas scheußlich schmecken...

message.en_US: But trust me, it's great!
message.pt_BR: Mas confia em mim, ele  timo!
